{"tid":2371581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工作繁忙，最新官方香港人 拍拖相處時間出爐！","createTime":"2021-01-19T03:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T02:57:40.000Z","uid":12628,"like":27,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"db5c97b0c1421c487612df5b3c70f79ec810e96c","tid":2371581,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"電話應該一日傾一次，每次限10分鐘，唔可以超時。講撚完就算！<br />\n<br />\n每日WhatsApp，tg, signal呢啲隨意，見人覆就講多句，見人無覆就唔好煩住人，人地有時間自然會覆！<br />\n<br />\n每星期見面一次，為時最好午後至晚上呢段時間，必須屌閪，飯只能食一餐，邊到爆房，食咩都可以傾，出街日男方比晒錢都可以。<br />\n<br />\n其餘時間，自己搞掂自己，珍惜自己私人時間！咪係到煩撚住晒，你咁大個人，應該有自己獨立嘅生活同思維，唔係咩都依靠人，要人陪！<br />\n<br />\n做個精明伴侶，保證拍得持久！"},{"pid":"031e3cac9a507718b1e66fe5c51f1a9ebe09e8bb","tid":2371581,"uid":193497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:55:07.000Z","msg":"係咪要定埋擁抱日"},{"pid":"a1f0819fe342924a3819a1bb8b16ac0bf58496b9","tid":2371581,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"031e3cac9a507718b1e66fe5c51f1a9ebe09e8bb","tid":2371581,"uid":193497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:55:07.000Z","msg":"係咪要定埋擁抱日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:56:42.000Z","msg":"可以考慮吓，仲要定埋抱好嘅時間唔可以超時"},{"pid":"20a39cd6b6582530115428127b7b24cd1a334b6d","tid":2371581,"uid":79471,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:58:13.000Z","msg":"一日一次傾電話會唔會太chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恐怖情人"},{"pid":"012ae950e47088b3909688c03219a89ff2fee5a9","tid":2371581,"uid":103347,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"中國人是要管的<br />\n<br />\n拍拖要拍成咁 咁多規矩 <br />\n寧願分手享受單身生活"},{"pid":"a1c3cca998787054d7b6939fefb26dc129acbe1b","tid":2371581,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20a39cd6b6582530115428127b7b24cd1a334b6d","tid":2371581,"uid":79471,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:58:13.000Z","msg":"一日一次傾電話會唔會太chur<img src=\"/a